title: Rita Ora looks unrecognisable as she steps out with bizarre new look: 'What's she done to her face?'
text:
She looks so different (Photo: Splash) Share Get daily updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email 
Rita Ora's fans have been left baffled by the star's brand new look. 
The America's Next Top Model judge, who's fuelled rumours she's dating Justin Bieber, stepped out looking unrecognisable yesterday. 
The Body On Me singer showed off a fresher-looking face while heading out in New York City days after attending the Fifty Shades Darker premiere. 
Looking demure in a rose-coloured gown, Rita's fans speculated that the star didn't look like her usual self. Fans don't recognise her (Photo: Splash News) 
One fan wrote on social media: "What has Rita Ora done to her face?" 
A second confused fan said: "So, Rita Ora bought herself a new face!" 
A third added: "Also what happened to Rita ora's face!??!" 
The former pop star, who hasn't released an album in over half a decade, has teased that she could be collaborating with one of the biggest stars in the world. She looks very different (Photo: Splash News) (Photo: RItaOra/snapchat) 
The America's Next Top Model host took to Snapchat to sing along to K-Ci and JoJo's classic ballad All My Life while Justin Bieber played the piano. 
Despite not performing a new song, fans immediately went into meltdown over suggestions that the pair could be working on new music together. Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
